External dependencies:

- Pretty printer: pprint
    http://gallium.inria.fr/~fpottier/pprint/pprint-20130324.tar.gz

- JSON serialization: yojson
    opam install yojson

- Network communication: ocurl
    opam install ocurl

  You need to have "libcurl" installed on your system. On Debian I had
  to do (the "libcurl-dev" package was ambiguous):
    sudo aptitude install libcurl4-openssl-dev

- Bit vectors implementation: bitv
    opam install bitv
